Product:{\"sku\":\"7100077279\"}.name: PICO PARK 2
Product:{\"sku\":\"7100077279\"}.description({\"html\":true}):
PICO PARK 2 is a 2D action-puzzle game where working together is key! We're now back with more levels than in the last game!

As with the previous iteration, this game can be played locally or online from two players all the way to eight. All levels can be played no matter how many players you have, so jump in with your friends and take 'em on!

Online play also features cross-platform support, allowing you to play with your friends no matter what platform you have! Also, up to 7 players can join online with a single Nintendo Switch™.

Added alongside the WORLD, ENDLESS, and BATTLE modes is the slightly unfair, somewhat difficult DARK mode! Jump, plot, and plunge into the all-new PICO PARK 2!
Product:{\"sku\":\"7100077279\"}.disclaimer:
Uma assinatura Nintendo Switch Online (vendida separadamente) e uma conta Nintendo são necessárias para partidas online. Não disponível em todos os países. Acesso à internet é necessário para funcionalidades online. Termos se aplicam. nintendo.com/online.

This game can also be played online with 2-8 players on the Nintendo Switch Lite.

©2024 TECOPARK
